How are we bringing IRL value to our NFT?

- Beer available to purchase online through our brewer (and future partners)
- Drinking tools: Beer bongs, beer pong sets, beer die sets
- Sponsoring college greek life and growing our community
- Partnering with bars and clubs

3/ 

The Bears

Booze Bears are randomly generated using over 300 drunken traits. All rarities are determined on-chain to ensure fair minting.
